title: Who's Afraid of the Six Bad Wolves?

media:group.media:title: Who's Afraid of the Six Bad Wolves?
media:group.media:description:
Exploring trauma through "The Path" video game. All profits from this video will go to the Trevor Project, an LGBT at-risk teen suicide prevention organization. If you'd like to make your own donation, you can at https://www.thetrevorproject.org/
--

A site for finding local suicide support groups:
https://afsp.org/find-a-support-group/

The Hotline, a domestic violence support group:
https://www.thehotline.org/

A collection of resources, support groups, and hotlines for victims of sexual assault:
https://www.nsvrc.org/sites/default/files/2014-09/nsvrc_publications_resource-list_online-resources-for-survivors.pdf

International Association for Suicide Prevention (Europe):
https://www.iasp.info/resources/Crisis_Centres/Europe/

International Association for Suicide Prevention (Africa):
https://www.iasp.info/resources/Crisis_Centres/africa/

The Trevor Project, a suicide hotline for LGBT teens: https://www.thetrevorproject.org/

Australian mental health support services:
https://www.respect.gov.au/services/

If you're unable to find a group here that you believe should be included, leave a comment or send me a message and I'll add it.
